CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 3, 1959, pg. A2 reads: "F. & A.M. Widows' banquet - Star of the West Lodge, 2, F.& A.M., sponsored its annual widow's banquet at Soldiers and Sailors Memorial Hall, Sept. 26. Among those present were Mr. and Mrs. Major A. Greene, Anna Watkins, Mrs. Edna Ingram, Mrs. Harriet Jackson, Emmanual Phillips, D.D.G.M.; Alan Williams, W.M.; Mrs. Alan Williams, Judge Loran L. Lewis, Lee A. Harris, D.D.G.M.; Mrs. Sara Walton, H.A. Walton, D.D.G.L.; and Joseph Givens, P.G.M., M.W.P.H.G.L. of Pennsylvania. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Man wearing dark suit, dark patterned necktie, and eyeglasses, standing at podium on banquet table in Soldiers and Sailors Memorial Hall during the Star of the West Lodge annual widow's banquet
